### Settlement is now integrated automatically into Remita, Interswitch, and RevPay transactions
### No separate endpoint needed - settlement happens after successful PIN/2FA validation

### Test Remita Transaction with Settlement
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/send/api/bgatesvc/v3/billpayment/biller/transaction/process
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "billPaymentProductId": "12345",
  "amount": 1000.00,
  "transactionRef": "REMITA_TXN_001",
  "name": "Test Customer",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "phoneNumber": "08012345678",
  "customerId": "CUST001",
  "accountNumber": "1234567890",
  "pin": "1234",
  "enforce2FA": false,
  "secondFa": "",
  "secondFaType": "",
  "channel": "MOBILE"
}

